# Write out LG in Gold by Jaseowns
# UO Outlands
# Description:  
#   This is for loot goblin.. it writes out LG in Gold using 30 coins.
#   Target a pouch or backpack that is not in your bag.
#   Edit the global timeout if needed, 600 ms worked for me
@setvar! placement
@setvar! globalTimeout 600

# Move any gold back to backpack
while findtype "gold coin" placement as gold
    lift gold 60000
    drop backpack -1 -1 -1
    wait globalTimeout
endwhile

if counttype "gold coin" backpack < 30
    overhead "Need at least 30 gold in bag to complete" 34
    stop
endif

